This is to inform that an advertisement on "Record date for issue of Bonus Equity shares" has been published today, i.e. October 18, 2024 in the following newspapers:

(i) The Times of India (English);
(ii) The Economic Times (English);
(iii) Navbharat Times (Hindi);
(iv) Maharashtra Times (Marathi)

The newspaper clippings are enclosed for information and records.

This is to inform you that the advertisement for "Extension of last date for payment of unpaid call money by holders of partly paid-up equity shares" has been published, in English language, today i.e. September 23, 2024 in the following newspapers:

All Editions:
(i) Times of India (English newspaper);
(ii) Economic Times (English newspaper);
(iii) Navbharat Times (Hindi newspaper);
(iv) Maharashtra Times (Marathi newspaper);
(v) Gujarat Samachar (Gujarati newspaper);
(vi) Sandesh (Gujarati newspaper); and
(vii) Divya Bhaskar (Gujarati newspaper).

The newspaper clippings are enclosed for your information and records.
